quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  39,57,Oba ogambe nti singa mazima Katonda yannungamya naalibadde mu batya (Katonda)
  39,58,Oba bwoliraba ebibonerezo oligamba nti ddala singa nnina okuzzibwayo nembeera mu balongoosa
  39,59,(olyanukulwa nti) nedda ebigambo byange byakujjira n'obirimbisa era neweekuza nooba owo mu bakaafiiri
  39,60,"Era ku lunaku lw'enkomerero abo abaayogera obulimba ku Katonda oliraba ebyenyi byabwe nga biddugadde (ate lwaki tebaliba batyo!), abaffe mu muliro Jahannama temuli nfo zaabo abeekuza"
  39,61,Era Katonda agenda kuwonya abo abaamutya nga abawa okwesiima kwabwe (olw'ejjana gyalibayingiza). Akabi (kâ€™ebibonerezo) tekagenda kubatuukako era bo ssi baakunakuwala
  39,62,"Katonda, ye mutonzi wa buli kintu era yye, ye mutambuza wa buli kintu"
  39,63,"Era yaalina ebiyimiriddeko entambula y'eggulu omusanvu n'ensi, ate abo abaawakanya ebigambo bya Katonda, abo bo be b'okufaafaaganirwa"
  39,64,"Bagambe (ggwe Nabbi Muhammad) nti: abange mmwe abatamanyi, ebitali Katonda bye mundagira mbe nga nsinza"
  39,65,"Ate nga mazima watumirwa obubaka n'eri abo abaakukulembera (nti) singa ogatta ku Katonda ebintu ebirala emirimu gyo gya kwonoonekera ddala, era ojja kubeerera ddala mu bafaafaaganiddwa"
  39,66,Wabula Katonda gwoba osinza era obe mu beebaza
  39,67,"(Abagatta ku Katonda ebintu ebirala) Katonda tebamussa mu kifo kimusaanira, so nga ensi yonna eriba mu kibatu kye ku lunaku lw'enkomerero, nga eggulu omusanvu gazingiddwa mu mukono gwe ogwa ddyo, musukkulumu era wa waggulu ku ebyo bye bamugattako"